title: AmigaOS3.5.iso
description:
Amiga Operating System 3.5 in an iso image format, can be burned to CD or mounted using any suitable program. It was the first Amiga OS to support CD drives out of the box.

Please note this is an Amiga Operating system only! You will also need an Amiga or an emulator to make use of it.

If using winUAE you will need to set it to be an  A1200 A3000 or A4000 with 3.1 rom for this to install.

Enjoy some retro computing fun :-)
